<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Olivia Culpo was summery chic when she was glimpsed out and about in Los Angeles this weekend.</p>

<p>The 28-year-old sensation was joined by her younger sister Sophia as she emerged from lockdown to go purse shopping.</p>

<p>Wearing her dark hair down in an attractive bob, Olivia slipped into a flowing white sleeveless blouse that perfectly suited the season.</p>

<p>Off she goes: Olivia Culpo was summery chic when she was glimpsed out and about in Los Angeles this weekend</p>

<p>The sizzling sensation, who was crowned Miss Universe in 2012, tucked the top into a fashionably torn pair of high-waisted jeans.</p>

<p>She cinched a belt around her trousers to emphasize her enviably trim waistline as she surfaced for her masked outing.</p>

<p>Meanwhile Sophia, who herself has more than 100,000 followers on Instagram, flashed her toned legs in a pair of bike shorts. </p>

<p>Sophia complemented the shorts with a stylish sweater and balanced on a pair of stilettos while ambling about with her sister.</p>

